{"tid":2209027,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"回帶， 香港警賊，污糟邋遢，色膽包天 2009年旺角警署內強姦非禮四少女","createTime":"2020-09-19T10:51:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-20T07:34:46.000Z","uid":333488,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b0adfed9010c3517e78588bf5e25b822f858d69e","tid":2209027,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:51:40.000Z","msg":"香港警察曾經「救急扶危，儆惡懲奸」的形象，或許一直以來都是市民一廂情願的看法。翻看新聞，這隊自詡正義的制服團體早已腐敗不堪。當年今日，2009年9月19日，《蘋果》報道一名香港警察色膽包天，誘騙四名少女到旺角警署，在認人室淫辱她們，更將其中一人強姦（<a href=\"https://hk.adai.ly/e/2uV2YL52R9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.adai.ly%2Fe%2F2uV2YL52R9&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE7%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=356739d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.adai.ly/e/2uV2YL52R9</a>）。<br />\n更令人嘩然的是這名警員被揭發後竟然亳無悔意，庭上審訊期間更不時露出微笑，行為令人髮指。這位當年年僅30歲的警員如何借職權犯罪？懲教署心理專家在心理報告如何描寫他？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母死黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95f41c97be692fd4663733745e072a7cfa9d83a7","tid":2209027,"uid":133033,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:54:16.000Z","msg":"香港警察由97後開始個準則就係恐怖分子先請<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b0aa3199ed90a37212e5577ec7ac4c98d686bf9","tid":2209027,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T10:54:29.000Z","msg":"補返條link <a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200809/TQWSLK52LRFYLJKXHGS7VLDVRI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FTQWSLK52LRFYLJKXHGS7VLDVRI%2F&d=1nW%2FAbATR%2BcU2iH%2BEMdxE7%2F5csivkdzoxKq11rtKUO4%3D&h=5a3045cf\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200809%2FTQWSLK52LRFYLJKXHGS7VLDVRI%2F&h=8b771bd1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/202008